plot: The Mandalorian and Child travel to an ancient site.

As instructed by Ahsoka, The Mandalorian arrives with Grogu in Tython, and finds the ancient temple on top of a mountain. He places Grogu at the center so that he may choose his path. While Grogu meditates trying to reach out with the Force, the Mandalorian is confronted by Boba Fett and Fennec Shand and then later by companies of stormtroopers under the command of Moff Gideon as he tries to protect the child.
